title: Bobby Gets Into Stranger's Car By Accident + Listener Seeks Advice On What To Do With Her Wedding Dress After Divorce
itunes:title: Bobby Gets Into Stranger's Car By Accident + Listener Seeks Advice On What To Do With Her Wedding Dress After Divorce
description:
Bobby tells the story of how he ended up in the wrong car with a stranger, thinking it was his Uber driver. The Girl Group discusses what a listener should do with her wedding dress after her divorce. Also, Amy's neighbors threw a late night party on a week night.
